Germany's RWE May Buy Turkish Hydropower Plants, Bid for Power Asset Sales

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-02-16T08:59:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/germany-s-rwe-may-buy-turkish-hydropower-plants-bid-for-power-asset-sales.html
  RWE AG  may buy privately-held
hydropower plants in Turkey and is interested in bidding for
power plant sales planned by the government, Andreas Radmacher,
chief executive of RWE  Turkey  Holding AS said at press
conference in Istanbul today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
